0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e17487a7e5942b230ac5dfa9e9d2c85674899568","tid":1464143,"uid":71262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"Set deadline ➡️大量文宣➡️政府冇回應➡️正式升級癱瘓機場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"同意。呢個pt係關鍵。分階段，唔回應就升級<br />\n1)  停航班 (可能一星期，甚至一個月) <br />\n2)  停入閘 <br />\n3)  停check in"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3232db6ce1195439c834a71e78ba6e809b47d8","tid":1464143,"uid":280899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"係室飽機場    係包和機場   唔係佔領機場      唔係癱瘓機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466104</a>"},{"pid":"a31b0e3b1eae9ca9ef48d758f3c9a493606cc2f3","tid":1464143,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:48.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"787d5e5ca5042ae170bfadf56c293430871b95fd","tid":1464143,"uid":32485,